sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipeline<br/>Component
    participant DSPUI as DSP UI / Query Client
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution / PutArtifacts<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS, Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT metadata records<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS, Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Commit confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutResponse (IDs assigned)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutEvents<br/>(link Artifacts to Executions)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT event records
    DB-->>MLMD: Commit confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutEventsResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutAttributionsAndAssociations<br/>(link to Contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT attribution/association records
    DB-->>MLMD: Commit confirmation
    MLMD-->>DSP: Response

    Note over DSPUI,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Metadata Retrieval (Lineage Query)

    DSPUI->>MLMD: GetLineageGraph / GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS, Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with joins<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol<br/>Optional TLS, Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (artifacts, executions, events)
    MLMD-->>DSPUI: Lineage graph / metadata response
